{"tid":349012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《香港獨立宣言》","createTime":"2017-08-06T08:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T13:14:53.000Z","uid":92301,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a83707e86d92ff40a1ff06754fb1b24a2ac5d15f","tid":349012,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"「我們不是沒有顧念我們中國的弟兄。我們一再警告過他們，他們的立法機關企圖把無理的管轄權橫加到我們的頭上。我們也提醒過他們，我們移民並定居來這裡的狀況。我們曾經呼喚他們天生的正義感和俠肝義膽，我們懇切陳詞，請他們念在同文同種的份上，棄絕這些必然會破壞我們彼此關係和往來的無理掠奪。對於這種來自正義和基於血緣的呼聲，他們卻也同樣置若罔聞。迫不得已，我們不得不宣布和他們分離。我們會以對待其他民族一樣的態度對待他們：戰時是仇敵，平時是朋友。」<br />\n<br />\n歡迎補完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db90e08639e77693a7610ae13721e9fc7e2f056","tid":349012,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0593f70289590efd0369d19524d083abdb7fb47","tid":349012,"uid":33307,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:23:56.000Z","msg":"有中國兩個字<br />\n冇香港兩個字<br />\n<br />\nfail"},{"pid":"356d91258f3c7702da2b1660c03dc95e0294747c","tid":349012,"uid":25643,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:26:33.000Z","msg":"用中文唔用粵文，fail"},{"pid":"da99c26f80790e19a67f4a7d318e588e8732b515","tid":349012,"uid":92301,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:25:50.000Z","msg":"請各位補完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69ad5251aff221c208f763dfd43c9b8083caa8d","tid":349012,"uid":40216,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:39:59.000Z","msg":"抄美國獨立宣言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd8c5ef4c33fad8581e4c5719caef1df8b80079","tid":349012,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T14:19:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抄美國獨立宣言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db329bec3a5e74d3b84294e40ce73c3f0f46e46f","tid":349012,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T14:26:12.000Z","msg":"弟乜撚兄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47f113b499b5ab9b791f6c524912c504c0eec49","tid":349012,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T14:29:41.000Z","msg":"可以用多啲本土啲既字句，不必執著抄美帝獨立宣言"},{"pid":"cac0defc3907931e8681983e7816bb4207a8a873","tid":349012,"uid":91721,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:14:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「我們不是沒有顧念我們中國的弟兄。我們一再警告過他們，他們的立法機關企圖把無理的管轄權橫加到我們的頭上。我們也提醒過他們，我們移民並定居來這裡的狀況。我們曾經呼喚他們天生的正義感和俠肝義膽，我們懇切陳詞，請他們念在同文同種的份上，棄絕這些必然會破壞我們彼此關係和往來的無理掠奪。對於這種來自正義和基於血緣的呼聲，他們卻也同樣置若罔聞。迫不得已，我們不得不宣布和他們分離。我們會以對待其他民族一樣的態度對待他們：戰時是仇敵，平時是朋友。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港，不是中國</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎補完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7535cca1ed4722ab50c166b58ea524ed054b0ca3","tid":349012,"uid":58358,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:42:24.000Z","msg":"同佢地並非同文，亦未必同種"},{"pid":"b5e82bf060d752bfe8387b17fe33cf938fb3b319","tid":349012,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a4f3502e33ed9376abaa544256d40b8e354568","tid":349012,"uid":93784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:10:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>「我們不是沒有顧念我們中國的弟兄。我們一再警告過他們，他們的立法機關企圖把無理的管轄權橫加到我們的頭上。我們也提醒過他們，我們移民並定居來這裡的狀況。我們曾經呼喚他們天生的正義感和俠肝義膽，我們懇切陳詞，請他們念在同文同種的份上，棄絕這些必然會破壞我們彼此關係和往來的無理掠奪。對於這種來自正義和基於血緣的呼聲，他們卻也同樣置若罔聞。迫不得已，我們不得不宣布和他們分離。我們會以對待其他民族一樣的態度對待他們：戰時是仇敵，平時是朋友。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港，不是中國</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎補完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n好多我們,他們 做乜鬼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1) 講歷史及政治背景 <br />\n2) 區分兩者不同 -&gt; 說明兩者信念,制度,價值觀等不同<br />\n3) 否定愛中國論, 統一論, 港中並非兄弟/母子等倫理關係<br />\n4) 共匪侵佔/破壞香港既種種事實/情況<br />\n5) 香港必須獨立建國, 重點係團結返香港人"},{"pid":"5dfca4b93eacab775342e1b7848a38f3fac3b185","tid":349012,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b75d139a19519247fb7de5690b41802b727a805","tid":349012,"uid":11970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:43:23.000Z","msg":"咩弟兄<br />\n血濃於水咩"},{"pid":"c851be00d19bd95ac0b2b5f7d2bf8e8be5a3e417","tid":349012,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T20:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4dad7303f16e42bd20d82cdea9334e11765b0f","tid":349012,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8b97f7af18e6cb6a1d069eaa4a35397e8594e7","tid":349012,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30670ac9fbc736b2438bf3a7603f774fd34fbb9","tid":349012,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:18:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89aa630a9202d99734f215a648a31a34f5fa8bf7","tid":349012,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:35:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cb48a649ed7ca620935242608b69af74f2226a0","tid":349012,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:46:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08588d004fe753249829c1b8828f671a83e78124","tid":349012,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:51:07.000Z","msg":"咁夜仲唔訓？聽日唔撚洗做啊？你邊間公司嫁？洗唔洗叫你老細俾多D OT你啊！"},{"pid":"0c44de82230605ef45d7434b3aa290e40ed4ad92","tid":349012,"uid":58358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"「我們不是<span style=\"color: red;\">不相信中國給香港一國兩制之承諾</span>。我們一再警告過他們，他們的立法機關企圖把無理的管轄權橫加到我們的頭上。我們也提醒過他們，<span style=\"color: red;\">中英聯合聲明有約束力及法律效力</span>。我們曾經呼喚他們<span style=\"color: red;\">謹餘之人性及合約精神</span>，我們懇切陳詞，請他們念在<span style=\"color: red;\">香港對其經濟重要性</span>份上，棄絕這些必然會破壞我們彼此關係和往來的無理掠奪。對於這種來自正義和基於<span style=\"color: red;\">友誼</span>的呼聲，他們卻也同樣置若罔聞。迫不得已，我們不得不宣布和他們分離。我們會以對待其他民族一樣的態度對待他們：戰時是仇敵，平時是朋友。」"},{"pid":"5abe4ebb12ca607bb593decce258ebc677f8f1de","tid":349012,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30033a522e0266f920c55ce6b25cf0ba27395d0d","tid":349012,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}